{"descriptions":[{"id":1257,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe suffixes \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་\u003c/span\u003e are combined with the auxiliaries \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབྱུང་\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡོད་མ་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e to make the following auxiliaries:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePast: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་བྱུང་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་བྱུང་སོང་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་བྱུང་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་བྱུང་སོང་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePresent: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་ཡོད་མ་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་མི་འདུག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eAll these auxiliaries have a modal sense, and may be translated in English by the modal verbs \u0026ldquo;to be able to,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;to have to.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྒྱུ་\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་\u003c/span\u003e may also be combined with the copulas \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརེད་\u003c/span\u003e to form future modal auxiliaries (xxlink 28.3.1 future modal).\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:21 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:21 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}